Wei Li

dcterms:description: The dataset contains 417 geometries of walls, with respective CFD simulations. The geometries have different center-offsets in relation to the wind inlet direction.
dcterms:title: Wall Dataset

dcterms:creator: Xiaoxiao Guo
Wei Li
Francesco Iorio
dcterms:description: The dataset contains 548 geometries of single buildings, with a fixed height. The geometries have the same parameterizations as the Wall Dataset in addition to varying length and width.
dcterms:title: Single Building Dataset

dcterms:creator: Xiaoxiao Guo
Wei Li
Francesco Iorio
dcterms:description: The dataset contains 658 geometries of two buildings, with a fixed height. Each building has different center offsets while having the same angle to the wind direction.
dcterms:title: Two Buildings Dataset

dcterms:creator: Xiaoxiao Guo
Wei Li
Francesco Iorio
dcterms:description: The dataset contains 474 geometries with the same parameterizations as the Two Buildings Dataset, except the height of the buildings are provided as an additional channel.
dcterms:title: Two Buildings with Varying Height Dataset

dcterms:creator: Xiaoxiao Guo
Wei Li
Francesco Iorio
dcterms:description: The dataset contains 287 geometries from the city center of Oslo, Norway. The geometries are more complex in shape and allow single buildings to have multiple height values.
dcterms:title: Real Urban City Environment Dataset
